            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aliquam imperdiet pharetra nunc at condimentum.</div>
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>
</code>  CSS:  <code>.outer {
  width: 200px;
  border: 1px solid #0f0;
}
.bad-table {
  width: 100%;
  border: 1px solid #f00;
}
.target {
  width: 100%;
  overflow-x: auto;
